data.description: Beautiful like new 1795 sq. ft. 3 bedroom, 2.5 bath home with loft in Plum Creek. Open floor plan with lots of windows and natural light. The kitchen boasts solid counter tops, large breakfast bar island, and gas cooking. Large master bedroom and bath with large walk-in shower and double vanity. Enjoy the covered front and back(12x9) patio. Plum Creek community has access to pools, dog parks, golf, playground, walk/bike trails, and a catch and release fishing pond. Close to I-35, shopping, hospitals, schools, and great restaurants. Wonderful clubhouse for residents uses. Playgrounds are walking distance to 4 awesome parks! This gated part of the community has paved walking paths that lead to the Golf Course & Pond. 20 min drive to Downtown Austin, 30 min to New Braunfels, and less than an hour drive to San Antonio.
